URL_249:
Patrons must leave no trace of any food, drinks, or beverages they opt to
bring into the Library. When considering bringing food into the Library, a
public space, patrons are expected to comply with the following guidelines:

URL_288:
any activity involving consumption of a food, liquid, alcoholic beverage, liquor,
                                 drug, or other substance that subjects the student to an unreasonable risk of harm
                                 or that adversely affects the mental or physical health or safety of the student;

any activity that induces, causes, or requires the student to perform a duty or task
                                 that involves a violation of the Code of Student Conduct; other university policies;
                                 or local, state, or federal laws.
